responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "3CA9D35C433ACE9AD81747AFA113832D", "The gobbun are a goblinoid species far evolved from the goblins of the Second Age. Highly intelligent and largely peaceful, the gobbun created a utopia in the far future of Verra. They maintain a sprawling metropolis that spans much of the orb. The are the last known intelligent species of Verra.")
